Command to log on to psql
-------------------------

psql -U postgres -d fitnesse_metrics_db

Command to create table
-----------------------

create table fitnesse_test (
     id integer,
     Test_name varchar(500),
     run_time_in_millis integer,
     run_date timestamp,
     status varchar(4),
     host varchar(40),
     ip_address varchar(16),
     branch varchar(40),
     sha varchar(40),
     run integer
);

Command to drop table
---------------------

drop table fitnesse_test;

